 S2  C           IAMAIS    IFLE 0
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    G4SKJY
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    G4SKHZ
     C                     MOVEL*DATE     G4KOHZ
     C                     MOVELPPUSER    G4KOME
     C                     Z-ADD@TIME     G4KOTM
     C                     SUB  IAMAIS    G4MAIS
     C                     UPDATGTCPP411
     C                     Z-ADD0         WWMAIS  30
