     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     IBKOHZ
     C                     Z-ADD@TIME     IBKOTM
     C                     MOVELPPUSER    IBKOME
     C                     UPDATGTBPL101
     C                     END
      *--------------------*
      * 2004.11.08 MSK     *
